<item>
            <title>[LU-6594] The o2iblnd option rnr_retry_count should be removed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6594</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The o2iblnd does not allow sender to overrun receive queue on the receiver - there&apos;s a credit mechanism to prevent that. So in theory the o2iblnd should never receive any RNR NAK. Therefore the rnr_retry_count option is not needed at all.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;rnr_retry_count should be removed as a module option&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Just in case, add some code to issue warnings should RNR NAK is ever received.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
